This means developers can now write in Go and deploy to C-compatible systems, opening up huge possibilities for embedded systems or low-level programming.

3
00:00:16,950 --> 00:00:22,612
It is a game changer for expanding Go's versatility and reach into new hardware environments.

4
00:00:22,612 --> 00:00:26,212
Imagine the possibilities for performance and portability!

